t117.text: I have concluded that I actually enjoy SPORT in general. Was (still am) a geek + nerd, so sport never really appealed to me until I first smashed a volleyball (inadvertently) at age 28.

t118.text: Test cricket used to bore the fuck outta me, but as I understood more about the game I understood that there’s a certain degree of overall grace that you need to play bloody good test cricket. Take your time, conserve energy, good defense, hold motivation until the last innings.
